Package controller

Class DataInitializer

java.lang.Object
controller.DataInitializer
public class DataInitializer extends Object
Loads and provides access to all core container lists used in the system, including applicants, officers, managers, projects, and various transactional records. All lists are initialized from their respective CSV files during system startup.
